      "workingSteps": [
        "√144 = 12 because 12 × 12 = 144",
        "∛27 = 3 because 3 × 3 × 3 = 27",
        "5³ = 5 × 5 × 5 = 125"
      ],
      "explanation": "Square root reverses squaring; cube root reverses cubing."
    },
